item.dc:creator: @Axiom_Owner Axiom Owner
item.description:
@Axiom_Owner wrote:

This is what i use…For server Run…

@echo off title AxiomScape RunServer java -Xmx512m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server
This is my Client Run…

@echo off @title Client cd Client "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe" -Xmx300m client 10 0 highmem members 32
